r />\n<br />\n咁俄羅斯同美國就可以繼續做地上最強，冇人敢挑戰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n北平和談已經想咁，同時史太林都想南北對峙，以長江為界。但係老毛知道可以徹底奪取全國，所以堅持打落去，最後簽字渡江。"},{"pid":"094710293fb8721928f7b3a036dfd355e047c8c4","tid":113031,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"點解要分? 扶值代理人分裂做2-3個國家更有利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過中國太多人，係要個共產黨管住班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743946c388224206f4570ad1ffe4e02659cd2623","tid":113031,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯同美國即刻崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}